---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | Dongho Lee Real Estate"
  description="Cookie Policy for Dongho Lee Real Estate."
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <header>
      <p class="page-kicker">Cookies</p>
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: July 13, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <section>
        <h2>What Cookies Are</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that may be stored on your device when you visit a website. They can help websites remember preferences, measure performance, and understand how visitors use the site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How This Website May Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses Google Analytics 4 to understand aggregate website usage, such as pages viewed, general traffic sources, and movement between donghotheagent.com and dongholee.ca. Google Analytics may use cookies or similar technologies to maintain a visit across these two related domains. This website does not use this analytics configuration to collect information submitted through contact forms.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Essential cookies or similar technologies needed for website hosting, security, and basic functionality.</li>
          <li>Google Analytics cookies or similar technologies that help us understand which pages are useful and preserve a visitor session between donghotheagent.com and dongholee.ca.</li>
          <li>Third-party embedded content, if present, such as maps, videos, or external media.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Blocking some cookies may affect how certain website features work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          Third-party services may use their own cookies or tracking technologies according to their own policies. This website does not control those third-party practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Questions</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about cookie use may be sent to <a href="mailto:contact@donlee.realtor">contact@donlee.realtor</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
